Transcript: Hi. This is Marilyn Shirley calling to invite you to a very exciting event on Sunday. February 15th, Jack Layton will be nominated as our federal candidate in Toronto Danforth. It begins at 5 p.m. at the upper house at 735 Queen Street East. We also plan to canvas every household in the riding earlier in the day. For more information call 416-591-5455 extension 233.
